# ❤️ Animal Breeding

Breeding is **NOT instant**.

During breeding:

🚫 Other players cannot enter.

A temporary **Privacy Zone** appears.

Breeding takes time depending on animal.

Possible rare babies:

⭐ Golden Animal

⭐ Albino Animal

⭐ Legendary Animal

Animals can grow old and die naturally.

