# 🌍 DreamVerse Connections

## 🍔 TasteCraft

HarvestVerse supplies:

- Wheat
- Rice
- Milk
- Vegetables
- Fruits
- Honey

TasteCraft converts them into food.

---

## 🏙 BuildVerse

If a BuildVerse city has no farms:

It buys food from HarvestVerse.

Examples:

5000 Wheat

2000 Milk

1000 Vegetables

As the city develops:

It can build its own farms.

Then imports decrease.

