# 👨‍🌾 NPCs

## 📊 The Market Analyst
- Demand aur Supply ka data analyze karta hai.
- Mostly accurate reports deta hai.
- Kabhi-kabhi apna profit secure karne ke baad report public karta hai.

---

## 🗣️ The Rumour Merchant
- Afwaah failata hai.
- Kabhi sach, kabhi jhooth, kabhi aadha sach.
- Market ko manipulate karne ki koshish karta hai.

---

## 🌱 Seed Seller
- Common, Rare aur Legendary Seeds bechta hai.
- Seasonal Seeds bhi available hote hain.

---

## 🐄 Livestock Dealer
- Animals kharidne aur bechne ke liye.
- Rare breeds bhi kabhi-kabhi available hoti hain.

---

## 🔧 Farm Mechanic
- Tractor aur machines repair karta hai.
- Vehicle upgrades bhi deta hai.

---

## 🚚 Delivery Manager
- Daily aur Special Orders deta hai.
- Delivery rewards aur bonuses manage karta hai.

---

## 🐾 Animal Doctor (Veterinarian)
- Bimaar animals ka treatment karta hai.
- Vaccination aur health check-up karta hai.

---

## 🚜 Co-op Manager
- Community Farming Contracts deta hai.
- Group missions aur team rewards manage karta hai.

---

## 👨‍💼 Agriculture Officer
- Government farming projects deta hai.
- Crop quality aur farming standards check karta hai.

---

## 🚛 Government Supply Officer
- Schools, Hospitals aur Government ke bulk food orders deta hai.

---

## 🎉 Festival Organizer
- Harvest Festival, Flower Festival aur Farming Expo organize karta hai.
- Festival-exclusive rewards deta hai.

---

## 🌦️ Weather Reporter
- Aane wale mausam ki forecast batata hai.
- Storm, Rain aur Heatwave ki warning deta hai.

---

## 🛒 Market Trader
- Rare items aur seasonal goods kharidta aur bechta hai.
- Kabhi-kabhi limited-time offers deta hai.

---

## 🎣 Fisherman
- Fishing quests deta hai.
- Rare fish aur fishing equipment bechta hai.

---

## 🌳 Forest Ranger
- Tree Plantation aur Nature Conservation missions deta hai.
- Rare saplings reward me deta hai.

---

## 🐝 Beekeeper
- Honey production aur Bee Farming sikhata hai.
- Rare Queen Bee milne ka chance deta hai.

---

## 🤠 Old Farmer
- HarvestVerse ka sabse experienced NPC.
- Beginners ko tutorials aur useful tips deta hai.
- Kabhi-kabhi hidden farming secrets bhi batata hai.

